                  <Font name="System Bold" size="12.0" />
               </font></Label>
            <Label fx:id="top3" layoutX="39.0" layoutY="118.0" prefHeight="89.0" prefWidth="245.0" text="A1: StuVent is an interactive navigation platform that connects School Events with Students in an easy to navigate way." wrapText="true" />
            <Label fx:id="top6" layoutX="355.0" layoutY="218.0" prefHeight="79.0" prefWidth="234.0" text="A5: Yes, in the &quot;Leaderboard&quot; and &quot;Profile&quot; tabs, it displays possible prizes a Student can win, depending on placement. " wrapText="true" />
            <Label fx:id="top9" layoutX="350.0" layoutY="297.0" prefHeight="125.0" prefWidth="179.0" text="A6: The school funds the prizes, usually with fundraising, so prizes can vary in size and cope. Some common ones are Electronics, Trips, and Awards" wrapText="true" />
