                  <Font name="System Italic" size="28.0" />
               </font>
            </Text>
            <Label fx:id="top31" layoutX="618.0" layoutY="110.0" prefHeight="89.0" prefWidth="245.0" text="A7: The points are judged at the end of every quarter, typically with a 1 week notice. " wrapText="true" />
            <Label fx:id="top32" layoutX="31.0" layoutY="234.0" prefHeight="89.0" prefWidth="245.0" text="2A: Students earn points by registering for Events. In the &quot;Upcoming Events&quot; tab, a student can register for any event listed, they will get a code to participate, and a confirmation code after the event, to recieve points" wrapText="true" />
            <Label fx:id="top23" layoutX="341.0" layoutY="289.0" text="Q6: What types of Prizes are there?">
