            </Label>
            <Label fx:id="top311" layoutX="31.0" layoutY="347.0" prefHeight="89.0" prefWidth="245.0" text="A3: No, Students can earn points by participating in events, which do not have a limit. However, it usually ends on a quarterly basis. " wrapText="true" />
